719433f-b.title: Manhattan: East End Avenue - 80th Street
719433f-b.text:
East End Avenue, east side, from East 81st (lefti to
80th (right) Street's, as viewed across the cleared
area on the westerly side of the Avenue. Behind these
structures is the new Drive and the East River.

No. 1-2
P. L. Sperr
